{"tid":1601208,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"澄清公告：上水珍苑麵家 唔係藍絲 仲曾經幫助因示威活動被退學學生揾學校","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T20:47:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a35d45571d55e03e563fbd03db7b37cf3c3d16b","tid":1601208,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"位於上水的珍苑麵家一向受歡迎，不少人特地為了其牛腩、豬手等名物慕名而來。然而近來的逆權風波中，有人在網上指麵家老闆是藍絲，曾出席撐警大會，雖然火速有網民為其抱不平，說老闆絕對不會撐警，但已引起不少爭議。<br />\n<br />\n上星期四，有網民指珍苑麵家絕不是藍絲，理由是老闆曾義助一名因活動而被退校的學生就讀第二間學校。記者上門查問，老闆梁先生表示，大約兩個月前，朋友及熟客已經通知他們，有網民指他曾出席撐警集會，對此他大呼冤枉。<br />\n<br />\n「我們怎會做這樣的事情，反而我太太或家人都有去遊行，支持年輕人，有時會去支持、派水。」至於為甚麼會被人指是藍絲，他表示不知情，但亦沒有特別去澄清，因為自覺不會說話，只怕愈描愈黑，還好因為做街坊生意，影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n雖然被抹黑是藍絲，但他們依然支持年輕人發聲，甚至替被退學的學生找學校。「那同學因為示威事件，而被校長踢出校，於是我太太就聯絡很多以前教育界的同行，直至找到一間中學可以去面試。」雖然沒有報酬，但是對他們而言這不過是舉手之勞。「因為如果是事件的年輕人，為香港發聲的，如果可以都應該幫幫他們。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20190928/Q2LQ5RUYRFKRKGAD2POPE4543I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20190928%2FQ2LQ5RUYRFKRKGAD2POPE4543I%2F&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=a5d0dee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20190928%2FQ2LQ5RUYRFKRKGAD2POPE4543I%2F&h=5d654b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20190928/Q2LQ5RUYRFKRKGAD2POPE4543I/</a>"},{"pid":"534df428453184541b845dc3a70efa932432130a","tid":1601208,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"你班暴徒仲唔快d懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食到佢無得賣"},{"pid":"1e83393d2a5274e11f4e2a9e96860edae7fe4518","tid":1601208,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0a0a8d4d304c6dd79b497f431dcf9b8700e4e9d","tid":1601208,"uid":207968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:10:19.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"be38c2bdd611ddc859942e349a94776048a2c32f","tid":1601208,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"0c375286238bc76a884fa8639f5106038fd1c22d","tid":1601208,"uid":156587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebd30ec132ac95c26f0805f706cfd470c30eb49","tid":1601208,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b24bad45557380a4c9a01414b6632e483b10f01","tid":1601208,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8291e5111d8b2c4ecf02e0e4b32daf29f5ca90ee","tid":1601208,"uid":317169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"534df428453184541b845dc3a70efa932432130a","tid":1601208,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"你班暴徒仲唔快d懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食到佢無得賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:47:11.000Z","msg":"不要說...暴徒<br />\n試著說...暴龍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為食暴龍"}]}